    - `id` (INT, PK, AI)
    - `verse_text` (TEXT)
    - `verse_reference` (VARCHAR)
    - `date_to_show` (DATE, UNIQUE)
    - `created_at` (TIMESTAMP)

#### [NEW] [Verse.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/LCMTVWebNew/backend/models/Verse.php)
